  "title": "Pilot and co-pilot spotted a UFO on the way to Porto Alegre [2012]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/05/pilot-and-co-pilot-spotted-a-ufoon-the-way-to-porto-alegre-2012/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-cX",
  "content": "<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span class=\"s1\"><strong>MAR 25th, 2012</strong>. Flying from Antonio Carlos Jobim Airport in Rio de Janeiro-RJ to Salgado Filho Airport in Porto Alegre-RS, the pilot and the co-pilot of flight GLO 1949 spotted an unidentified flying object about 30 meters long in size, resembling a dark balloon and traveling at a speed of over 700km/h. Witnesses spotted the UFO from a distance of approximately 5 km. The trajectory of the object that was at an estimated altitude of 38,000ft went in the Northeast direction.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo &#8216;Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)&#8217;. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.683. &#8220;</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado (ovni) em Foz do Iguaçu, Paraná&#8221;. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our &#8216;Info&#8217; page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [&#8220;Código de Referência&#8221;] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n",
